      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve as a dependable daily driver for an owner who doesn't mind a bit of character. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and the car drives reliably, there is visible wear and tear consistent with its age. You'll find some minor cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and the interior shows signs of regular use. It is a solid, functional choice for someone looking for affordable transportation that still has plenty of life left in it.",
