      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of distinguished character and proven mechanical integrity. This specimen has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a reliable and sophisticated driving experience. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, it offers exceptional utility and performance for the discerning driver. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that balances functional excellence with refined styling.",
